fields.description:
When the {{network.httpclient}} test suite is run in Drillbit, the {{largeFileWithRedirect}} test fails consistently with the error {{Not Found}}. The platform that the test is run on doesn't seem to matter, we get this same failure in both Android and iOS.

If you try going to the URL in the test, you'll see a not found error:
{code}
http://www.appcelerator.com/download-win32
{code}

We need to update this URL to a relatively large file (a few MB will do) that has a working URL
